they can navigate

00:14:08.630 --> 00:14:09.980
relative to each other.

00:14:09.980 --> 00:14:12.310
So you could think in your mind
about all the different

00:14:12.310 --> 00:14:15.790
possible combinations of looking
at the Command Module,

00:14:15.790 --> 00:14:18.090
looking at the Lunar Module,
looking at the Earth, a

00:14:18.090 --> 00:14:19.380
million different things
you can do.

00:14:19.380 --> 00:14:23.270
And it was an supremely
flexible program

00:14:23.270 --> 00:14:25.630
that they could use.

00:14:25.630 --> 00:14:26.880
Here's another view.

00:14:30.400 --> 00:14:31.930
